changelog: Finally the first online version of Foobe was released. The functionalities are basic: List of users, being able to add them as contacts and see them in a list in the profile. You can also add information from your business profile.
Updating explanatory sections of the site, registration of 2 users, while expanding the database.
Tradeshows attendance calendar updated after the events on the Covid-19
A detailed information of you contacts in your contact list, updating and making us growth

Registered members will now be able to add their company's website and be congratulated on their birthday. In addition, 3 new sections are in preparation, which are messaging between users, a currency converter with a quote and history, and lastly, statistics from different indices and price and quantity indicators around the world.
